                <p style="margin-bottom: 3rem; font-size: 20px; line-height: 2; color: #f1f5f9;">I've been getting tons of questions about AI stem splitting lately, and honestly, I get why people are confused. There's a lot of misinformation out there, and most producers are missing out on what could be the biggest breakthrough in their mixing process.</p>

                <p style="margin-bottom: 3rem; font-size: 20px; line-height: 2; color: #f1f5f9;">Let me break this down for you in a way that actually makes sense.</p>

